<a href="javascript:;" class="more"> 等人赞同</a>


</div>
<div class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="3295781" data-action="/answer/content">

<div class="fixed-summary zm-editable-content clearfix">     必须是纣王.<blockquote>     帝辛是帝乙之子，有雄才，致力于用兵东南；牧野之战中周文王之子周武王在距离朝歌（今河南淇县）七十里外的牧野击败商军，商帝辛登上鹿台，“蒙衣其珠玉，自燔于火而死”，商朝灭亡。《左传》称：“纣克东夷而陨其身”。<br></blockquote>武松打虎好歹还有个短棍,增加10点攻击力与10%攻击速度.而这货直接就裸奔去了,所谓“材力过人，手格猛兽”.(殷本纪)<br><img src="http://pic3.zhimg.com/d0202273373e2b4ebc2c4060fb2653e2_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="259" data-rawheight="194" class="content_image" width="259"><b>手格猛兽</b><br>力能扛鼎算什么,这货是拽着九牛走,手撑着屋顶换柱子,所谓"倒曳九牛，抚梁易柱".(帝王世纪)<br><img src="http://pic3.zhimg.com/cb5de7a937c1339bcb11e22840f4fe1e_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="417" data-rawheight="204" class="content_image" width="417"><b>倒曳九牛</b><br><img src="http://pic1.zhimg.com/5937d0443cf79381972ab01615fb0284_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="284" data-rawheight="177" class="content_image" width="284"><br><br><b>抚梁易柱</b><br>熊也不在话下,有记载"伸钩索铁，手搏熊虎"(帝王世纪)<br><img src="http://pic3.zhimg.com/a434c3be46d4c52ade6bd09722644d62_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="259" data-rawheight="194" class="content_image" width="259"><br><b>伸钩索铁</b><br><b><img src="http://pic2.zhimg.com/4d21ed067184ee43f7c22eddbc82ffb5_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="421" data-rawheight="300" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="421" data-original="http://pic2.zhimg.com/4d21ed067184ee43f7c22eddbc82ffb5_r.jpg">熊虎<br><img src="http://pic4.zhimg.com/5af1218514ae7cd4334cdf00619ce203_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="677" data-rawheight="635" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="677" data-original="http://pic4.zhimg.com/5af1218514ae7cd4334cdf00619ce203_r.jpg">纣王的手博指南</b>
<a href="/question/27782159/answer/38187562" class="toggle-expand">显示全部</a>
<div class="fixed-summary-mask"></div>
</div>

</div>
</div>
